=head2 ServiceAccountName => Str

The name of the service account that's used to run the pod. For more
information, see Kubernetes service accounts
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/eks/latest/userguide/service-accounts.html)
and Configure a Kubernetes service account to assume an IAM role
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/eks/latest/userguide/associate-service-account-role.html)
